{"tid":1680877,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葛珮帆批評港台節目偏頗　梁家榮：港台持平客觀不偏不倚","createTime":"2019-10-29T05:29:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T05:55:45.000Z","uid":200758,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c3b451d58cbfcab7717f22b9f7887fb7ea8cc2cb","tid":1680877,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:29:52.000Z","msg":"多名建制派議員在資訊科技及廣播事務委員會質疑，港台的節目偏頗及有政治立場。民建聯葛珮帆批評，港台在反修例事件製作的節目「仇中」及「仇警」，容許與港獨有關的人士發表言論，散播暴力仇恨。廣播處長梁家榮表示，港台作為公共廣播，恪守準確、持平及客觀的原則，不偏不倚讓各方表達意見。他舉例說，在電台節目有不同人致電，不會偏幫任何一方。對於旅遊界議員姚思榮質疑港台電視節目，例如《鏗鏘集》及《頭條新聞》偏向示威者，沒有報導事件對市民生活影響及警方壓力等，梁家榮表示，從電台峰煙節目及論壇的統計，近幾個月邀請的建制派人士比非建制多，不能篩選各人在節目上的言論，但觀眾用不同角度聆聽有不同感受，應該用製作標準衡量是否有資料錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n2019-10-29 12:48:27 (1)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488794-20191029.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488794-20191029.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP9%2FsvSzfkBtT%2Fd%2Bxj92WHuQ%3D&h=84f151cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488794-20191029.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7afcc2d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488794-20191029.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"dcc5ef3a8a400ee4e3384e92c07e7aa4dfb88fd4","tid":1680877,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:30:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zyBfyPB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzyBfyPB.jpg&h=2708f4ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mtm3RDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMtm3RDU.jpg&h=fd9c9c47&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1a2b5dfdff873627c244bc657e88b9c35daed590","tid":1680877,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:33:14.000Z","msg":"咁CCTVB呢 <im